    <!-- Application Structure Plan: A single-page portfolio with a top navigation bar. Sections include an impactful hero 'Home', a skills section with a visually striking chart, an interactive 'Projects' gallery with a multi-column layout and hover effects, and a stylized vertical 'Experience & Education' timeline. This structure is designed for a seamless, scroll-based narrative, allowing for both quick scanning and deep exploration. The dark theme with vibrant accents provides a modern, high-tech feel. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
        - Skills: Report Info -> Technical Skills -> Goal: Visually showcase strengths -> Viz: Horizontal Bar Chart (Chart.js) -> Interaction: Custom tooltip styling and responsive resizing -> Justification: Provides a clean, modern, and easily scannable representation of skills. The vibrant colors in the dark theme make the data points stand out.
        - Projects: Report Info -> Project descriptions -> Goal: Organize & Detail -> Viz: Grid of Card-based elements (HTML/Tailwind) -> Interaction: Filter buttons, subtle hover scale/shadow animations, and clickable cards to a project portfolio site -> Justification: Encourages exploration and allows users to quickly filter by technology, making the content relevant to their interests. The animations add a layer of polish, and the clickable cards provide a direct path to more detailed work.
        - Experience/Education: Report Info -> Work History & Education -> Goal: Show chronology & milestones -> Viz: Stylized Vertical Timeline (HTML/Tailwind/CSS) -> Interaction: Scroll-based animation for visual entry -> Justification: Breaks up the page with a strong vertical design element, making career progression clear and visually interesting.
        - CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
